metadata.name: Bowie Stratified, 2021
metadata.description:
Outtake created from an accident that happened along the way to making ‘Bowie Explosion’ on KnownOrigin. I hit the wrong application in the software program. But I liked the way it looked so I extracted the reference image, painted it and put the artwork back in to the piece. 

Stored on Arweave, minted on Manifold custom contract.
